<!-- O Clube Privado (Concept) -->
<section class="py-section-gap-mobile md:py-section-gap-desktop bg-track-asphalt relative reveal-hidden reveal-visible" id="experiencia">
  <div class="px-gutter max-w-container-max mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-stack-lg md:gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1 relative">
        <div class="aspect-[4/5] relative bg-pit-lane-navy border border-white/5 overflow-hidden group">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-50 z-0"></div>
          <img alt="Steering wheel detail" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center mix-blend-luminosity opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-700 z-10 relative" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBNS-l2eSNDOU8fX2IBTOpw9XyLU1CDOcjUYpF4CSvyfM6-8bofvb58BQ5oqvWC2XFlbTf_HnidBF5krpswmm73_R-dOa35_bzP7U4YblnCziJ92MDEYcpFZ6jvgrw6P2wRs2O3NtkSOSp5vhSZ0RsRiJ9A7oe9TZdr_LVjWRn54rUQnnWWhGF-gLs7GsVTBb27yjgj0ppDA7AnMTZG9tZvdxfqcKpBthXC8jiYFYKuRjd3eBeoElDB7bpYw2nEHlg3EGxM6nfacfk=w2560"/>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full p-6 bg-gradient-to-t from-track-asphalt to-transparent z-20">
            <p class="font-label-caps text-microcopy text-primary tracking-widest">PERFORMANCE & CONTROLE</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Decorative element -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 w-24 h-24 border-l-2 border-b-2 border-primary hidden md:block z-0 transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-110"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="order-1 md:order-2 flex flex-col justify-center">
        <h2 class="font-section-title text-section-title text-performance-white uppercase mb-6">
          Muito além de um <span class="text-primary block">Track Day.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-metallic-grey mb-6">
          O Interlagos Private Track Club não é um evento aberto ao público. É uma plataforma de relacionamento de alto nível, desenhada especificamente para C-Levels, fundadores e investidores que valorizam seu tempo e seu círculo de contatos.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-metallic-grey mb-8">
          Substituímos o ambiente caótico dos eventos tradicionais por um ecossistema controlado, focado em duas métricas: precisão na pista e qualidade nas conexões geradas nos boxes.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 pt-6 border-t border-white/10">
          <div>
            <span class="block font-hero-headline-mobile text-[32px] text-primary mb-1">40</span>
            <span class="font-label-caps text-microcopy text-metallic-grey tracking-wider uppercase">Vagas por Edição</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="block font-hero-headline-mobile text-[32px] text-primary mb-1">100%</span>
            <span class="font-label-caps text-microcopy text-metallic-grey tracking-wider uppercase">C-Level & Founders</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
